{
  "stem": "23498.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was-- he could only stay in a lying position.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't have anything to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother, at this time, was in Pruszkow as a servant working for someone else.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a Dutch, Polish-Dutch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she-- because she was so nice-looking and so on, she went there, and she said to the-- she was very badly fed also, because they were very mean, you know?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was working hard and just had enough to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she was collecting a bit of food every month to get-- or every few weeks-- to get to my father.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she couldn't, because it was a front line.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she got that German officer, and she said, look, this is my house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have to get some things, because I have nothing to live from.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he gave her a pass to go there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she got there, and she brought him some lard, you know, some fat, and some bread, which he kept because he was like that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And what saved him, it-- it was the-- was-- with the sausage, they used garlic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a lot of garlic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So the-- the bread was bad, but he ate it piece by piece together with garlic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he had a small bottle of vodka and one apple.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that apple, he kept.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And all of a sudden-- that was a few times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then she couldn't go anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "All of a sudden, and-- and up at the top were all Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he had to go to-- out to get fresh water.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what they did, they knew that someone is there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they put cotton-- cotton around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If the cotton will be broken, it means that someone-- but my father was very careful.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
